description: Home of the original "Hilly City Hot" Happy Jack's is the cart for you if you're looking for the best hot dogs around! Hot dogs have been the family business for generation, and you can tell there's a lot of love here when you bite into one of Happy Jack's delicious hot dogs or sausages! For a taste of tradition that's full of flavor, look for Happy Jack's Hot Dogs today!
name: Happy Jack's Hot Dogs
